<LegalLayout title="Cookie Policy | Slimkay" description="How Slimkay uses cookies and similar technologies, including Umami analytics.">
  <h1>Cookie Policy</h1>
  <p class="updated">Last updated: 8 May 2026</p>

  <p>This site uses limited cookies and similar technologies to keep the website useful, reliable, and measurable.</p>

  <h2>Analytics</h2>
  <p>We use Umami analytics to understand page views and basic website usage. Umami is configured through the Slimkay website ID and is loaded only in production builds.</p>

  <h2>Essential Technologies</h2>
  <p>The website may use normal browser and hosting technologies required to serve pages, media, fonts, and form requests.</p>

  <h2>Managing Cookies</h2>
  <p>You can block or delete cookies through your browser settings. Some browser changes may affect how websites remember preferences or load third-party services.</p>

  <h2>Changes</h2>
  <p>This policy may be updated if the site adds new analytics, marketing tools, embeds, or booking technology.</p>
</LegalLayout>
